---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Products"
  description="Explore GraceSoft products including Capture, Sentinel Concierge, Sentinel Cook, and RSVP, built for practical business operations and reliable day-to-day execution."
>
  <main class="services-page">
    <section
      class="title-section services-hero relative isolate overflow-hidden text-white px-4 py-20 sm:py-24 lg:py-28"
    >
      <div
        class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-5 text-center reveal rise"
      >
        <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight sm:text-4xl lg:text-6xl">
          GraceSoft Products
        </h1>
        <p
          class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-sm text-gs-purple-100 sm:text-base lg:text-xl"
        >
          Productized systems designed by GraceSoft for clarity, reliability,
          and practical business outcomes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="capture-spotlight-section px-4 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-8 sm:space-y-10">
        <h2
          class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-center reveal rise"
        >
          Featured Products
        </h2>

        <div
          class="grid gap-4 sm:gap-5 grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3"
        >
          <article class="feature-card reveal rise delay-1 space-y-4">
            <p class="capture-kicker">GraceSoft Capture</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold sm:text-2xl">
              Capture, organize, and act faster
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gs-black-700">
              GraceSoft Capture helps teams collect and structure key
              information so operations stay clean, searchable, and easier to
              execute.
            </p>
            <p>
              <a
                href="https://capture.gracesoft.dev/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="capture-primary-link inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-5 py-3 font-semibold"
              >
                Visit GraceSoft Capture
              </a>
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="feature-card reveal rise delay-2 space-y-4">
            <p class="capture-kicker">GraceSoft Sentinel Concierge</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold sm:text-2xl">
              WhatsApp FAQ and booking AI agent
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gs-black-700">
              Part of the Sentinel AI suite, Concierge answers blueprint-based
              FAQs and supports booking workflows that respect business hours
              and public holidays.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gs-black-700">
              Works with Google Calendar, Apple Calendar, and Outlook
              calendar-based scheduling flows.
            </p>
            <p>
              <a
                href="https://concierge.sentinel.gracesoft.dev/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="capture-primary-link inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-5 py-3 font-semibold"
              >
                Visit Sentinel Concierge
              </a>
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="feature-card reveal rise delay-3 space-y-4">
            <p class="capture-kicker">GraceSoft Sentinel Cook</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold sm:text-2xl">
              Culinary and menu workflow assistant
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gs-black-700">
              Sentinel Cook supports food and beverage teams with guided,
              practical assistance for recipe and menu-oriented operations.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gs-black-700">
              It helps teams run kitchen and menu tasks with more consistency,
              clarity, and day-to-day reliability.
            </p>
            <p>
              <a
                href="https://cook.sentinel.gracesoft.dev/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="capture-primary-link inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-5 py-3 font-semibold"
              >
                Visit Sentinel Cook
              </a>
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="feature-card reveal rise delay-4 space-y-4">
            <p class="capture-kicker">GraceSoft RSVP</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold sm:text-2xl">
              Event RSVP and guest response microsite
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gs-black-700">
              GraceSoft RSVP helps teams collect and manage event responses in a
              simple, branded flow that keeps guest data organized and easy to
              act on.
            </p>
            <p>
              <a
                href="https://rsvp.gracesoft.dev/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="capture-primary-link inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-5 py-3 font-semibold"
              >
                Visit GraceSoft RSVP
              </a>
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="services-detail-section px-4 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gs-purple-50"
    >
      <div
        class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 text-center"
      >
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl reveal rise">
          Product Naming Made Simple
        </h2>
        <div class="feature-card reveal rise delay-1 space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">
            GraceSoft product names are intentionally plain and structured so
            business owners can instantly understand what each offering does.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">
            Format: GraceSoft + Product Name + Function Name (optional).
          </p>
          <p>
            <a
              href="/product-naming"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-gs-purple-300 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-gs-purple-700 transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-gs-purple-50"
            >
              Read Product Naming Convention
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section px-4 py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
      <div
        class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 text-center cta-panel reveal rise"
      >
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
          Want One of These in Your Business Flow?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg">
          We can help you implement, customize, and operationalize the right
          product for your team.
        </p>
        <p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-gs-purple-700 bg-white rounded-md px-5 py-3 shadow-sm transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:opacity-90"
            >Talk to GraceSoft &rarr;</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
